direction: right

customer: 1. Customer sends message
connector: 2. Connector receives it
normalize: 3. Convert to NormalizedMessage
check: 4. Check duplicate and idempotency
save: 5. Save contact and conversation
queue: 6. Queue processing job
hermes: 7. Hermes reads approved context
extract: 8. Classify and extract lead data
update: 9. Update lead and create tasks
draft: 10. Draft next reply or action
approval: 11. Ask for approval when required
outbox: 12. Put approved reply in outbox
send: 13. Send through original channel

customer -> connector -> normalize -> check -> save -> queue -> hermes -> extract -> update -> draft -> approval -> outbox -> send
